      "text": [
        "293 - وَبِإِسْنادِهِ عَنْ عَلِيِ‏ عَلَيْهِ السَّلامُ قالَ: مَن كَذَّبَبِشَفاعَةِ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ لَمْ تَنَلهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.dr-ali-peiravi": [
          "31-293 According to the same documentation on the authority of Ali (a.s.), “Whoever denies the intercession of God’s Prophet (S) will not benefit from it.”"
        ]
      }
    }
